{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "16.1",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d98ef316",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃんっ！　ほらほら、早く！　こっちこっち～っ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c8e1ac5c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そんなに慌てるなって、人ごみの中で走ると危ないぞ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "42579044",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今日はお祭りがあるとスゥに誘われ二人っきりでやってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ce3cc39b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "夜は昼に比べ気温も落ち着き幾分か過ごしやすい。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b758f6c0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも人混みのもたらす暑さに汗が全身からじんわりと滲む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "188ae87b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥも俺と同じなのか、俺の手を引くスゥの手が僅かに汗ばんでいる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.1",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "31804750",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃん、見て見て！　カワイイ綿あめ！　すごく大きいね～♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9317c06f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "確かに大きいな。俺の頭より大きくないか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.1",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "29e75b9a",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "そうかも♪　でもあんなに大きな綿あめ見るの初めて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8caadb6f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "せっかくだし買ってみる？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.1",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8e11fc85",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "いいのっ！？　じゃあ二人で一緒に食べよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16e07aa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺は屋台のおじさんに綿あめを二つ注文すると、手慣れた様子で綿あめを作り始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.0",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b7060689",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最初は何も付いていなかった木の棒に徐々に絡まっていく白くフワフワしたモノ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "39.0",
      "line_index": 39,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5bc22fb5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "子供の頃それを見るのが好きだったが、大人になった今でもどこかワクワクしてしまう、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ef6f84e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "綿あめにはそんな魅力があるような気がした。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f2687ab",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ほら、スゥ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "239850fb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "出来上がった綿あめをおじさんから受け取ると、スゥにそれを手渡す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6f3c29a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺とスゥでは身長差があるので常に腰をかがめており少し辛い。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "47.0",
      "line_index": 47,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a980c7e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもスゥの笑顔を見たいと俺はそれを我慢していた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.1",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "bd2685a7",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "えへへ♪　ありがとう、お兄ちゃん。うわぁ～……本当に大きいね～♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3820bed7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして俺は自分の分を受け取ると、二人でベンチに座り仲良く綿あめを頬張った。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.1",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e6cfa3ac",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "もう食べちゃった……あんなに大きい綿あめだったのに、すぐに無くなっちゃうね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "779d0ae5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そうだな……でもそれだけ美味かったってことなんだと思うよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.1",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2e7cbcbc",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "そうだね、美味しかった！　お兄ちゃんと一緒に食べたからかな？　えへへへ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7fcc76dd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そうだな、二人で一緒に食べたから……ん？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.1",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c58d79a2",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "……お兄ちゃん？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21fca55e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（変わったデザインだな……ああいう浴衣もあるのか……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f123c45",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（浴衣とか普段見ないからつい視線が向いてしまうな）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.1",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e44813dc",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "（お兄ちゃん、また女の人見てる……スゥが傍にいるのに……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7d5580",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "よし、それじゃあ他の場所も見て回るか！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.1",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b01ac475",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "そっ、そうだね♪　それじゃあ行こ、お兄ちゃんっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.1",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e001babb",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "（お兄ちゃんと一緒にお祭りに来れたのはいいけど、お兄ちゃんの心を奪う泥棒猫が多すぎだよ……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.1",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "165f445b",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "（でも負けないもん……お兄ちゃんはスゥだけのお兄ちゃんなんだから……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.1",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fe850211",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "わぁ……何これ？　宝石みたいにキラキラしてる……キレイ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e8a79e1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥはとある屋台の前で足を止めると、色とりどりのフルーツ飴を瞳を輝かせながら眺めていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "101.0",
      "line_index": 101,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a923cfca",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "おお……！　懐かしい……！　これ俺の星にも同じのあったよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.1",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "edfc2146",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "へ～……ねぇ、なんでフルーツがキラキラしているの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "105.0",
      "line_index": 105,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7d1a59f5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "フルーツを飴でコーティングしているんだよ。それでキラキラしているんだ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.1",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "31bbfdfd",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "そうなんだ～……こんなのもお屋台にはあるんだね～……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.0",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "85ebcddd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "じゃあ買うか？　俺も久しぶりに食いたいし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.1",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1f1180b",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ホント！？　やった！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "32fd616f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "じゃあどれがいい？　好きなの選んでいいから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.1",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6e532d3",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "んー……そうだなぁ～……お兄ちゃんはどれが好きなの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "110b0d77",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺はリンゴかな……ほかのも好きだけど、リンゴが一番美味いと思ってる",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.1",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "38ace7e6",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "それじゃあスゥもそれにするっ！　お兄ちゃんが好きな物はスゥも好きになりたいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c291ea3d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "わかった、それじゃありんご飴二つね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.1",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "21b99529",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "んぁ、か、硬いっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "73dc46fe",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ははっ、飴だからな。こう、カブって勢いよく嚙みつくんだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.1",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "df3a0e94",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "勢いよく……あ～ん……あぐっ！　ううう、あぐ、うぐぅっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c5bf84b4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥは目いっぱい口を開け、再度チャレンジする。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "678d0a64",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしスゥの小さな歯では歯が立たないようで、りんご飴は綺麗な形のままだった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.1",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "be0ee78d",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "硬い～……！　食べられないよぉ～……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f51391f6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まぁそんなに慌てて食べなくても、ぺろぺろ舐めながら飴溶かしていけばいいんだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.0",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d8b2ec88",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "個人的にはガリガリ飴嚙み砕きながら食べるのが好きではあるけど",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.1",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4464e92f",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "それじゃあお兄ちゃん、お手本見せてよーっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.0",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ba5c2c2c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いいぞ、ガブって一撃で仕留めてやる……あー……あむっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.1",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "20e66c26",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ふあっ！？　お兄ちゃんすごいっ！　本当に噛み砕いて食べてる……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "efecf18c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ばき、かしゅ、と心地よい音と共にスゥの差し出したりんご飴を頬張る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.0",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aa03244c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "口の中に広がる子供の頃を思い出させる懐かしさを感じる甘さが、口の中いっぱいに広がっていった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5172e30e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ん～……甘いなーっ。でも懐かしい優しい甘さだ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.1",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7953dda5",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "あ……！　お兄ちゃんストップ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.0",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3688c954",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ん……どうしたんだ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.1",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b5eb98ee",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ちょっと屈んでくれるかな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f244dc8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ、いいぞ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.0",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5cb055c2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥに言われるままに屈むと、目線がスゥと同じになる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.1",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "282be0b7",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "じっとしててね、お兄ちゃん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ee8334cf",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "すっ、スゥ……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.1",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c39eb6cb",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ちゅ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a15ed447",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "んんんっ……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5edb97d7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（す、スゥの唇が……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3ef15aba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突然スゥはキスをし、俺は驚きのあまり固まってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.1",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f46a410e",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "あま～いっ♥　お兄ちゃんの言う通り優しい甘さだね～っ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.0",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "715657b4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、甘い……？　あっ、もしかして唇に飴付いてた……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.1",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a8aec4df",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "うんっ♥　えへへ、お兄ちゃんびっくりしててちょっと面白かった♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.0",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf0543a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そりゃいきなりキスなんて……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.0",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b7b06c4f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うう……ま、まだ心臓バクバクしちゃってる……スゥとキスするの初めてってわけじゃないのに……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
